      About
      4.5
      Excellent
      22 reviews
      Location
      Cleanliness
      Service
      Value
      Featuring free WiFi, AC in all rooms, Free Continental breakfast, OYO Townhouse 30 Sussex offers accommodations in Paddington, London, 0.7 miles from Hyde Park. The rooms include a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. At the hotel, the rooms are equipped with a desk. The private bathroom is equipped with a shower and free toiletries. All guest rooms at OYO Townhouse 30 Sussex feature closet and in room Iron facility The reception can provide advice on the area in order to help guests plan their day. Oxford Street is 1.1 miles from OYO Townhouse 30 Sussex. London City Airport is 9 miles from the property. Westminster Borough is a great choice for travellers interested in shopping, parks and history. We speak your language!
